The paper deals with image segmentation using machine learning techniques, specifically for electron microscopy (EM) images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of active learning and label propagation techniques, which are common in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of classifiers, which are commonly used in neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses segmentation results, which may involve natural language processing (cs.CL) techniques.
